4
00:01:06,046 --> 00:01:22,195
Seeing none, I will hand it off to Vice President Paris. Thank you, Madam President. You know over the past year, especially, we've been seeing around the city budget process and a number of issues, the inability of the city council to

5
00:01:22,195 --> 00:01:39,003
affect proper oversight over the city administration, and to build a collaborative processes where we can work together and one of the main reasons behind that is that the city charter doesn't really give the council much authority on those matters. So,

