So when we sat together as a unit, as the body that's elected us, we sat and said, you know, we don't see eye to eye in some things, and that's okay, as long as we respect it. But when Councilor Beas brought up, Vice President Beas brought up this proposal, for someone that's at the beginning, totally was so for charter review, the need for charter review was so important, it was one of my top three initiatives.

